data.description: This well cared for property is an idyllic weekender hideaway or perfect for a primary residence. Located 75 miles from Manhattan, Relland Farm is a true gem! It is an opportunity to both reside and operate businesses in one location. Having a riding and boarding academy and/or an Air B&B make it a rare find and a spectacular opportunity! Gracefully situated on 6 acres of picturesque land in the Arlington School District, this captivating equestrian property posses a charming 1930s farmhouse, three barns, five paddocks, one riding ring and an inground pool. The farmhouse is over 2000 sqft and offers 4 bedrooms and 1.5 baths. The first floor includes a kitchen, mudroom, formal dining room, half bath, sizable living room and office with fireplace. If need be, the living room and office can be used as a first floor bedroom suite. On the second floor reside bedrooms and a full bath. A first floor woodstove adds to the extreme efficiency and charm of the farmhome. The barns are plentiful and provide space for horse stalls, tack rooms, equipment, hay, livestock and more chicken coops. The paddocks are attached to buildings, have run ins and electricity. Add to the versatility of the property by finishing the barns into living spaces or indoor event centers. The property has housed 15-20+ horses and other animals at any given time, making it very unique and a very valuable. The 900 acre Tyrell Park is so close by and can be used as an extension for equestrian enjoyment. Private schools including Millbrook School, Dutchess Day School, Trinity Pawling and Oakwood add to additional options for education. The Taconic State Parkway is within 5 minutes and within 10 miles is the train station where Amtrak and Metro-North make travel to NYC and Albany and beyond easy. The enchanting town of Millbrook is 10 minutes away and offers shops, cafes, coffee houses and a farmer's market. Enjoy day trips to other captivating Hudson Valley towns too like Millerton, Beacon, Rhinebeck and New Paltz which offer more boutique shops, restaurants, coffee shops, theaters, galleries and music venues. This property is a spectacular, limitless opportunity in the Hudson Valley! Bring your imagination, your heart, your dreams and surround yourself by nature's beauty and tranquility as you make this property your own!
